{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_07_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 予想外の反応",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、うちらに会いに来てくれてありがとう\n暑いから、ちゃんとお水飲んで倒れんようにな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank y’all for comin' to see us.\nIt’s hot‚ so make sure y’all drink water and don’t get heatstroke.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、トリエルと集まってくれたみんなで\n一緒に最高の夏フェスの思い出を作ろうな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ let’s make some amazing summer festival memories\nwith TRINITYAiLE and everyone here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "――では、次の曲です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Now‚ onto the next song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏フェス終了後　舞台袖",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the summer festival‚ backstage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2866666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 21
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です～\n今日のうちらのステージ、どうでした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san‚ great job today!\nHow did y’all like our stage today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 21.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはいつも凄いけど……観てて楽しかったよ\n優がいつもより伸び伸びしてるように見えた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is always amazing‚ but it was really fun to watch.\nYu‚ you seemed more relaxed than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 35.7160266558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うち、普段から我慢なんかしてませんけどね\nでも……正直ほっとしたのはあるわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t usually hold back‚\nbut… I did feel relieved today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7826984088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 44.0493599891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんに、うちの好きなこと\nやっと言えたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I finally got to tell Rui-chan and Sumire-chan\nabout what I like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4493650754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 49.1493599891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "同人誌も夏フェスも、みんなで一緒にやれて\n最高の夏になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing fanzine and the summer festival together\nmade it the best summer ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9726403236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.3826933224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、同人誌即売会の会場も\n夏フェスに勝るとも劣らぬ、凄い熱気だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ the fanzine event was just as intense as\nthe summer festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。{user}さん\n今まで行ったことなかったんやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ right. {user}-san‚\nyou’d never been to one before‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8602492969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.7602442105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "存在は知ってたけど、足を運ぶ機会がなくてな\n俺は流行ってる漫画を時々読むくらいだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew about them‚ but never had the chance to go.\nI occasionally read popular manga…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "優の同人誌は、好きな漫画の二次創作って聞いたけど\nどういう話なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard your fanzine is fanfiction of\nyour favorite manga. What’s it about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.5180673918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ～、{user}さん\nそれ聞いてしまうん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san‚\nyou really wanna know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8514058115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.8514007252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがうちに興味持ってくれんの\n嬉しいわ～。ほな、軽～くご説明いたしましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m happy you’re interested in what I do.\nAlright‚ lemme give you a quick rundown.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4847391448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 93.1180673918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "人間社会に紛れてるモンスターを\nばっさばっさと斬り倒していく話やねんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about monsters hiding in human society‚\nand they get sliced and diced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8847391448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "バトルシーンがそりゃもう格好良くて\n戦いの裏にある人間ドラマもこれまた最高なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The battle scenes are super cool‚\nand the human drama behind the fights is just amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1354914666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 106.5513997079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "それぞれが抱えた想い、譲れないもの\nそこにバトルが合わさってめっちゃ盛り上がるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has their own unyielding desires and dreams‚\nand the battles amplify that excitement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6847381276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "さらには、尊敬していた兄との別れがあったり\n命を賭けて仇を討ち取った後の切ない心情とか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a touching farewell with a respected older brother\nand the bittersweet feelings after avenging a comrade――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7659884952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.8847350758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "あかん、脳内再生しただけで涙が出てくるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just thinkin’ about it makes me tear up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8847350758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、その漫画のうちの推しキャラ\n{user}さんに似てるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and you know what? My favorite character in that manga\nkinda looks like you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6514068288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 130.9180684091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、キャラっぽくセリフ言ってくれませんか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you say a line like that character? Please!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9180684091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺がか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 135.5252792758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、色々頑張ったうちへのご褒美やと思って！\n表情はそうやね……ちょっとアンニュイめな感じで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C'mon now‚ think of it as a reward for all my hard work!\nLet's see… Your expression should be a bit more… melancholy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7875130099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfesstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 146.5586126091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "「しょせん俺達は、戦いの中でしか生きられない」\nさあ、どうぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"In the end‚ we can only live within the battles we fight.\"\nGo on‚ give it a try!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9586176954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
